     FAAMWP80 IF  E                    DISK
     FAAMWP81 O   E                    DISK                      A
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WTIME
     I                                        1   60WJFB
     I                                        1   20TIMHH
     I                                        3   40TIMMM
     I                                        5   60TIMSS
     I                                        7  140WTIHZ
     I                                        7  100WTIYY
     I                                       11  120WTIMM
     I                                       13  140WTIDD
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W$PGM
     I                                      244 253 W$WSID
     I                                      254 263 @@USER
     I                                      264 269 W$JBNO
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *   PLIST                                            *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           POUT    1
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *   KLIST                                            *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *
     C                     TIME           WTIME
      *
     C                     READ AAMWP801                 81
     C           *IN81     DOWEQ'0'
     C                     EXSR #SB500
     C                     READ AAMWP801                 81
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *-----------------------------*
      *データ出力                 *
      *-----------------------------*
     CSR         #SB500    BEGSR
      *
     C                     CLEARAAMWP811
     C                     MOVELW0BMON    W1BMON
     C                     MOVELW0SHN1    W1SHN1
